HEADWORD: Skitty
<hw>Skit"ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Skittish</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A rail; as, the water
rail (called also <altname>skitty cock</altname>, and <altname>skitty
coot</altname>); the spotted crake (<spn>Porzana maruetta</spn>), and
the moor hen.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

